# ━━━ REQUIRED ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# Telegram Bot (create one via @BotFather on Telegram)
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC-DEF...
TELEGRAM_BOT_USERNAME=my_bot

# Your Telegram User ID (get it from @userinfobot on Telegram)
ALLOWED_USERS=123456789

# Your email address — required for Web UI magic-link login
OWNER_EMAIL=you@example.com

# Bot instance name (shown in Web UI)
INSTANCE_NAME=my-bot

# MySQL (created automatically by docker compose)
MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=change-me-root
MYSQL_USER=bot
MYSQL_PASSWORD=change-me-bot
MYSQL_DATABASE=claude_code

# JWT Secret for Web UI sessions (min 32 characters)
JWT_SECRET=change-me-jwt-secret-min-32-chars

# Internal API secret (backend <-> frontend communication)
INTERNAL_API_SECRET=change-me-internal

# ━━━ OPTIONAL ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# Web UI public URL (for magic link emails)
# PUBLIC_URL=https://your-domain.com

# Custom ports (defaults: backend=8080, frontend=3000)
# BACKEND_PORT=8080
# FRONTEND_PORT=3000

# Timezone (default: UTC)
# TZ=Europe/Berlin

# OpenAI API Key (enables image generation + TTS)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google Gemini API Key (enables image generation + TTS)
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AI...

# GitHub Personal Access Token (optional — enables gh CLI for Claude Code)
# GH_PAT=ghp_...

# SMTP (enables magic-link login for Web UI)
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=you@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASSWORD=app-password

# ━━━ OPTIONAL SERVICES ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Activate via: docker compose --profile <name> up -d

# Knowledge Graph (Neo4j) — activate with: --profile graph
# NEO4J_PASSWORD=change-me-neo4j

# Web Search (SearXNG) — activate with: --profile search
# (no config needed, just enable the profile)

# Reverse Proxy (Caddy) — activate with: --profile proxy
# (configure your domain in Caddyfile)
